  "title": "Junior Marketing (Resume BOOST! Fresh-Grads, no-exp welcome!!)",
  "description": "<p><strong>🎯 Junior Marketing OPENING</strong><br>\n <em>Fresh Grads Welcome | No Experience Needed | Immediate Start</em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Ready to dive into the world of sales &amp; marketing? We’re looking for creative, driven individuals to join our team as <strong>Junior Marketing Executives</strong> — no experience needed, just your energy and willingness to learn!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Do:</strong><br>\n📣 Support and execute business marketing campaigns <br>\n🎨 Work with brands - RESUME BOOSTER!<br>\n📊 Help track campaign performance and market trends<br>\n🤝 Work with a fun, supportive team to bring ideas to life</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What We Offer:</strong><br>\n✅ Full training &amp; mentorship<br>\n✅ A creative, vibrant, and fast-paced work environment<br>\n✅ Opportunities for career growth and skill development<br>\n✅ Fixed hours with work-life balance<br>\n✅ Fresh ideas and fresh grads highly encouraged!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Who You Are:</strong><br>\n✨ Full of ideas and curiosity<br>\n✨ A team player with strong communication skills<br>\n✨ Ready to learn, grow, and make an impact</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>🎉 No portfolio? No problem. Just bring your spark!<br>\n📩 Apply now and kickstart your journey with us!</p>",
